Freesdhost   How do I burn it to DVD to play in my Home DVD player Please help every copy of this movie i have  burned and play in my home it  just Rolls & Rolls  but other DVD's play Fine Thank you   SOS SOS

If you're using a PC, get a copy of Nero 7 Reloaded.  Use "Nero Vision" to encode the DivX file to a DVD image and burn it to a DVD disc.
Make sure you select the correct encoding in the 'options' (PAL or NTSC).  As this DivX was created from a PAL dvd, it will default to PAL.  Converting it to NTSC will take longer!
